                <img src="assets/img/player/safari.svg" alt="safari">
                <img src="assets/img/player/edge.svg" alt="edge">
                <h4>Browser Support</h4>
                <p>It is interoperable with the latest desktop and mobile browsers and has been thoroughly tested to deliver performance and reliability across the widest possible range of browsers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <div class="feature-block">
                <img src="assets/img/player/1554390.png" alt="img">
                <h4>API</h4>
                <p>Extensive documentation, sample code, and tutorials for initial introduction make it easy for new and old developers to get up to speed quickly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <div class="feature-block">
                <img src="assets/img/player/5023026.png" alt="img">
                <img src="assets/img/player/6478235.png" alt="img">
                <h4>MP3/MP4</h4>
                <p>Supports reading audio and video, including MP3 and MP4.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <nav class="feature-nav">
